Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H242B85&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara had completed blueprints for GOD's\NRS Device, which can convert any matter into energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanbara escaped GOD and tore the blueprints\Ninto nine pieces to entrust to his old colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD has stolen one of the pieces,\Nand the X Rider holds five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus does a deadly race for the\Nremaining three pieces begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Arise! King Dark!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Nasu Rindou Lake Family Ranch{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that music coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get it for me!\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, your mommy's calling you.\NCome on, it's looking stormy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bye-bye!\N-Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Nasu Family Ranch Management Office{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-The doll's moving!\N-Where are you going? Bad baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Lizard Viking, of GOD's Villain Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a cute little girl! Will\Nyou let Uncle Lizard see that doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No! She's my baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How precious! You know, Uncle\NLizard just loves little girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, let me give you a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat's fast on her feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mako!\N-Chiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, are you alright?\N-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better take her back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Can you get our stuff?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss!\N-Boss, come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A lizard did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like GOD to me, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what would GOD\Nwant with that doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably some secret to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me see your doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll give her right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen, I'm a friend of Dr. Nanbara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hidden a very important\Nblueprint inside this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever's listening to this,\Nplease protect the bluepri--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to find her\Nbefore it's too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use running, dear!\NCome and get your hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let her get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry and bawl all you want, darling!\NNow, will you give me that doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you treat an\Ninnocent child like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you... Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Trample him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Rider! Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:10:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}Historic Site - The Killing Stone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let her go!\N-One move and she dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Help!\N-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's one of my good points! Now, hand over\Nthe doll and change back if you want them to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, X Rider? What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Lizard Viking! I am impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You honour me, King Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all that remains is to finish Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, milord! I'll enjoy every second of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But show me the blueprint first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't there, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...It's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You imbecile!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl... I'm going to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing! Have you seen\Nthose two girls who helped you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD caught them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-GOD!?\N-The man too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They got Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And this was inside my doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece of Dr. Nanbara's\Nblueprints! Come on, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck are we stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...Alright. Take me to Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to him... once\Nyou give me the blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI don't have any blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm scared!\N-You're not getting away again... Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiko, do you really think Keisuke'll come!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come! I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs18\i1}Mashiko Pottery Direct Sales Office{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother struggling, Jin Keisuke. There's\Nsomeone I'd like you to meet. Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief!\N-Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that!\NTake Jin Keisuke to the kiln!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Block the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiko!! Mako!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss!!\N-Boss!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! Keisuke's coming! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, maybe I can melt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold fire a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke is dead! Nobody can\Nsave you now! Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, take aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the end...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You enjoy torturing people,\Ndon't you, Lizard Viking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how you like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rider!\N-I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't get away! Chief,\Ntake care of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster! He's gaining on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial Hell Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Daddy, mommy!\N-Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're ok, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! Another one lost to the X Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surrounded by failures!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that if I want the job done...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will have to do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace has returned to the peaks of Nasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But a new plot is already forming\Naround the last blueprint pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman comes to Nasu with blueprints for\NJin Keisuke, but Ant Capone is after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's Vacuum Hell Wheel\Nexplodes in the Nasu Highlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Showdown! King Dark Versus X Rider"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.08,0:23:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.08,0:23:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider